𝗗𝗮𝘆 𝟰𝟭: 𝗧𝗶𝗺𝗲𝗯𝗼𝘅𝗶𝗻𝗴 - 𝗦𝗮𝗰𝗿𝗲𝗱 𝗼𝗿 𝗙𝗹𝗲𝘅𝗶𝗯𝗹𝗲?
🧠 𝗧𝗼𝗽𝗶𝗰: Timeboxing drives focus, but should it ever flex?
🙎🏼‍♀️ 𝗠𝘆 𝗣𝗲𝗿𝘀𝗽𝗲𝗰𝘁𝗶𝘃𝗲: Timeboxing helps maintain discipline, but adaptability can unlock valuable insights in critical moments.

💡 𝗘𝘀𝘀𝗲𝗻𝘁𝗶𝗮𝗹 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝗜𝗻𝘀𝗶𝗴𝗵𝘁𝘀 (𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀) 𝗳𝗼𝗿 𝗦𝗰𝗿𝘂𝗺 𝗧𝗲𝗮𝗺𝘀 & 𝗦𝗰𝗿𝘂𝗺 𝗠𝗮𝘀𝘁𝗲𝗿𝘀! Harness expert strategies, proven best practices, and actionable tips to amplify collaboration and drive agile success to new heights
